data.description: Step into this inviting 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with an upstairs bonus room in the Farmington subdivison. The freshly painted interior breathes new life into this space, creating a vibrant and welcoming atmosphere. With a large covered front porch, screened-in back patio, fully fenced yard, and bonus room, this property offers versatile living options. New HVAC, water heater, gutters and more in 2023. New roof in 2019. Located close to shopping, restaurants, 295 and Fort Liberty. Don't miss the opportunity to make this home your own!
